-- UniCredit, Sensi Family May Agree on Roma Deal by Thursday, Sole Reports
-- Jerrold Colten
-- 2010-07-06T05:52:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/unicredit-sensi-family-may-agree-on-roma-deal-by-thursday-sole-reports.html

          
          
             The Sensi family may agree to hand
over ownership of Compagnia Italpetroli SpA, which controls
soccer club AS Roma SpA, to lender UniCredit SpA by July 8, Il
Sole 24 Ore reported, without saying where it got the
information.  
          
          


  


        